INCORRECT_USERNAME: Name should not be in camel case or more then 2 words
INCORRECT_EMAIL: Email should be in such format: example@example.example
INCORRECT_AGE: It should be number between 18 and 65
INCORRECT_PASSWORD: Password's length should be minimum 6 and maximum 12 symbols
INCORRECT_BIRTHDAY: Birthday should be in such format: 1997/07/18
INCORRECT_LOGIN: Login date should be in such format: 08 September 2018
INCORRECT_NOTIFICATION: Notification date should be in such format: 07-Sep-18
